.\n\n```\nparam ret\n\nraw: returns ((ra, dec), (ra, dec), ...)\n\nmean: returns (<ra>, <dec>)\n\nbrightest: returns (ra, dec)\n\nlatest: returns (ra, dec)\n\nparam filters\n\nfilters to apply to photo points\n```\n\nGet the position of the brightest PhotoPoint in the ZTF G band:\n\n```\ninstance.get_pos(\n        \"brightest\",\n        {'attribute': 'alTags', 'operator': 'in', 'value': 'ZTF_G'}\n)\n```\n\nGet the position of the latest photopoint with a magnitude brighter than 18\n(or an empty array if no photopoint matches this criteria):\n\n```\ninstance.get_pos(\n        \"lastest\",\n        {'attribute': 'magpsf', 'operator': '<', 'value': 18}\n)\n```\n", "TODO: improve"]}, {"name": "ampel.view.LightCurve.LightCurve._get_datapoints", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "filters", "type": {"name": "None | OneOrMany[JDict]", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "of_upper_limits", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "None | Sequence[DataPoint]", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ampel.view.LightCurve.LightCurve._apply_filter", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "datapoints", "type": {"name": "Sequence", "xref": {"fqname": "collections.abc.Sequence", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "DataPoint", "xref": {"fqname": "ampel.content.DataPoint.DataPoint", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "filters", "type": {"name": "None | OneOrMany[JDict]", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Sequence", "xref": {"fqname": "collections.abc.Sequence", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "DataPoint", "xref": {"fqname": "ampel.content.DataPoint.DataPoint", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["---\nraises ValueError: if datapoints is None or in case of bad filter values\